.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, azure, amber, chestnut, white
There are 5 different nationalities: indonesian, mexican, polish, chinese, nigerian
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, whitemaster, havana, davidoff, pall-mall
There are 5 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-fanta, fanta, soy-milk, iced-tea
5 different pets are kept: pony, ferret, hamster, lizard, goat

1. the indonesian is the person who likes grey
2. the mexican is the owner of the pony
3. the person drinking lemonade is the person who likes azure
4. the polish is the person drinking almond-fanta
5. the person who likes azure is to the right of the person who likes amber
6. the baccarat-smoker is the owner of the goat
7. the whitemaster-smoker is the person who likes chestnut
8. the person drinking fanta is in the middle
9. the chinese is on the far left
10. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret
11. the whitemaster-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the lizard
12. the davidoff-smoker is the person drinking soy-milk
13. the nigerian is the pall-mall-smoker
14. the chinese is to the left or right of the person who likes white

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   chinese	|    polish	|     indonesian	|    mexican	|    nigerian	|
| Color		|    chestnut	|      white	|      grey	|     amber	|     azure	|
| Beverage	|     iced-tea	|      almond-fanta	|      fanta	| soy-milk	|     lemonade	|
| Cigar		|     whitemaster	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| davidoff	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     ferret	|     lizard	|     goat	|     pony	|     hamster	|
